  "texts": [
    "where H(q) denotes the computed uncertainty score for a question q using Equation 10.",
    "After selecting the samples the small model troubles the reasoning, the next step is transferring knowledge from the LLM to the small model.",
    "This process involves using the LLM to generate pseudocompletion to fine-tune small model.",
    "To achieve this, we introduce a customized LLM-annotated explanation revision technique.",
    "This approach leverages the advanced capabilities of the LLM to provide customized guidance to the small model by allowing the LLM to detect and correct flaws in the small model's reasoning."
